<title type="html"><![CDATA[10/6(Sat.) How China's ‘social credit score &amp; 10 biggest tech companies in the world(Host: Krista)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=213&amp;p=227#p227"><![CDATA[
10/6(Sat.) How China's ‘social credit score &amp; 10 biggest tech companies in the world(Host: Krista)<br />How China's ‘social credit score’ will punish and reward citizens<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://bigthink.com/stephen-johnson/a-look-at-chinas-orwellian-plan-to-give-every-citizen-a-social-credit-score">https://bigthink.com/stephen-johnson/a- ... edit-score</a><!-- m --><br /><br /><br />1. What do you think about social credit score systems in china? <br />2. Is a social credit system a bad idea or good idea for Chinese govenment to manage their 1.4billion citizens? <br />3. Do you think surveillance cameras are an invasion of privacy? Why or why not?<br />-----------<br />What are the 10 biggest tech companies in the world?<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://trendingstock.today/what-are-the-10-biggest-tech-companies-in-the-world-2/">https://trendingstock.today/what-are-th ... e-world-2/</a><!-- m --><br /><br /><br />1. How many tech companies do you know in the article? <br />2. Are you a fan of these tech companies?  What do you think about their services or products? <br />3.What are the pros and corns of the growth of technology? <br />4. How technology affects your life?<br /><br />Agenda<br />7:00-7:30 free talk<br />(Session 1)<br />7:30-7:35 Opening remarks/ Newcomers self-introduction/ Grouping<br />7:35~ 8:15 discussion session (40 mins)<br />(Session 2)<br />8:15 ~9:00pm discussion session (45 mins)<br />9:00~9:30 free talk<br /><br />Position: Dante coffee Shop (丹堤咖啡), MRT板南線 - 新埔站2號出口, next to 7-Seven, <br />板橋民生路二段237 號, <br />Time: PM 7:00-9:30, <br />minimum charge of Dante coffee for Royal English club attendant NT$80 (丹提低消80元)<br />最自由的全英文會話聚會,前三次不用交會費,加入會員終生會費NT$500.請帶著開放與熱情來學英文<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=872">Shuman</a> — Wed Oct 03, 2018 9:39 pm</p><hr />
